query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.info in ('where now','plot','article','LD disc format','mini biography','agent address','tech info','LD label','production dates','languages','novel','LD number','essays','studios','LD frequency response','LD review','biographical movies','LD quality program','LD audio noise','birth name') AND (t.title like '%prophecy%' OR t.title like '%shield%' OR t.title like '%battle%' OR t.title like '%shoe%') AND t.production_year > 2004 AND mi_idx.info > '6.0' AND mi.info in ('English','Icelandic','Georgian','Serbo-Croatian','German','Flemish','Spanish','Galician','Afrikaans','Tatar','Danish','Ukrainian') AND n.name not like '%y%' AND n.name not like '%P%' AND n.gender in ('m') AND (k.keyword like '%death%' OR k.keyword like '%quest%' OR k.keyword like '%escape%' OR k.keyword like '%magic%' OR k.keyword like '%battle%') AND cct1.kind not in ('cast','complete+verified','crew')
